assay_description: Inhibition of bovine pancreatic alpha chymotrypsin
Inhibition of bovine pancreatic chymotrypsin assessed as proteolysis using N-succinyl-Gly-Gly-Phe-p-nitroanilide substrate incubated for 30 mins prior to substrate addition

Inhibition of human neutrophil elastase assessed as proteolysis using N-(methoxysuccinyl)-Ala-Ala-Pro-Val-p-nitroanilide substrate incubated for 15 mins prior to substrate addition measured every 30 seconds
Inhibition of porcine pancreatic elastase assessed as proteolysis using N-succinyl-Ala-Ala-Ala-p-nitroanilide substrate incubated for 15 mins prior to substrate addition measured every 30 seconds
